    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 DESPA，这是一款残酷、霓虹闪烁的竞技场射击游戏，为那些“下班后压力比空闲时间还多”的战士打造。没有废话，没有空档，只有钢铁、速度与复仇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/2cf55ab5412fe64e3050ba90125faefd.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/76be7903a3a3193e8636708a27ef43f9.poster.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/76be7903a3a3193e8636708a27ef43f9.webm?t=1764968250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即时匹配，7 分钟一局。眨眼就死。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公平辅助瞄准：手柄或鼠标，技术说了算。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >140 tick 服务器。延迟？不存在的。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/029020931bbed30446f6aa1b6612e838.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/76a46fd9c15106575646fd6806862a84.poster.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/76a46fd9c15106575646fd6806862a84.webm?t=1764968250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >疾跑、跑墙、抓钩。如果你不在移动，你就在输。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里是竞技场。它不在乎你是谁，只在乎你怎么杀。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/abfedb4bbf27f8c6c01f55ae15273e8f.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/3504467219644c3ff0bd1c2ad397d13b.poster.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/3504467219644c3ff0bd1c2ad397d13b.webm?t=1764968250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >智能重生点会把你刷在干掉你的那家伙背后。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有怜悯。没有规则。没有人性。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/ad15c2ccc3c88c9ad983a68123b490e5.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=80 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/76be7903a3a3193e8636708a27ef43f9.poster.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/76be7903a3a3193e8636708a27ef43f9.webm?t=1764968250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次击杀都重要：获得勋章来解锁狠角色皮肤。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 分钟日常任务。第二杯浓缩咖啡时就做完了。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝无氪金变强。永远不会。只有看起来致命的装备。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/37fa211d7b933cc000b8ee4ce454d5d7.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/5b4a96da7917897cef27337bd3648c1d.poster.avif?t=1764968250\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/5b4a96da7917897cef27337bd3648c1d.webm?t=1764968250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >老派灵魂，2026 级肌肉。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一枪都靠本事。每一次爆头都很私人的。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为速度而生，为混乱而造。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>如果你的 PC 扛过《毁灭战士 2016》，那就准备好了。</strong> 你呢？</p>",
